Subject: Hand Drumming for Beginners
Description: Hand drumming for beginners focusing on Middle Eastern and drumming for dancers. Bring a drum. Extra drums may be available.  Speakers include:Dan Eakin, Roni Neal  - Track: Music  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: Homesteading for the Begininer
Description: Interested in learning how to live a more self-sustaining life?  Come and see how you can get started on the homesteading path from two experienced homesteaders.  Learn how they got started and what they have found to work.   Speakers include:Dan Eakin, Matthew Grieshop - Track: Eco  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: Beekeeping for Sustainable Farming and Homesteading
Description: An introduction to beekeeping for homesteading.  Learn the tools of the trade, best practices, and harvesting techniques.    Speakers include:Dan Eakin - Track: Eco  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: Vermicomposting
Description: Worms are our friends, especially when they help us get rid of the mountians of compostable trash in our lives.  Learn how to keep your worms happy and your compost pile healthy.   Speakers include:Dan Eakin - Track: Eco  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
